product_specification.Other Display Features: 60Hz Refresh Rate, 20:09 Aspect Ratio, 89.5% Screen-to-body Ratio, 120Hz Touch Sampling Rate, Brightness: 360 nits (Min), 400nits (Typ), NTSC 70% (Typ) Color Saturation, Sunlight Screen Support, COG Sealing Process
product_specification.Primary Camera Features: 8MP Rear Camera, f/2.0 Aperture, 4P Lens Number, CMOS Sensor, 1/4 inch Sensor Size, 1.12um Pixel Size, AF, Photography Functions: Panoramic View, Portrait Mode, Expert, Timelapse, HDR, Beauty, Filter
product_specification.Secondary Camera Features: 5MP Front Camera, f/2.2 Aperture, CMOS Sensor, 1/5 inch Sensor, 1.12um Pizel Size, 3P Lens, FF, Photography Functions: Portrait Mode, Beauty Mode, HDR, Face-Recognition, Filter
product_specification.Video Recording Resolution: Rear Camera: 480p, 720p and 1080p (at 30fps), Front Camera: Default 720p (at 30fp), Support 480p (at 30fps), CIF (at 30fps)
product_specification.Sensors: Magnetic Induction Sensor, Light Sensor, Proximity Sensor, Gyro-meter, Acceleration Sensor
product_specification.Other Features: eMMC5.1 ROM, OTG Storage Formats: FAT32, EXFAT, NTFS, Charging Protocol and Power: BC1.2 10W, Reverse Charging Power: 5V 1.3A, LTE 2x2 MIMO, Phone Lock Functions: Face Unlock, Password Unlock, Pattern Unlock, Google Smart Lock, Private Protection, Night Shiled, APP Market
product_specification.Audio Formats: AAC, HE-AAC v1, HE-AAC v2, AMR, AWB, MIDI, MP3, OGG VORBIS
product_specification.Warranty Summary: 1 Year Warranty for Mobile and 6 Months for Accessories

product_description.5000 mAh Battery: The realme Narzo 50i runs on a 5000 mAh battery that offers up to 43 days of standby time. Also, it has a Super Power Saving Mode that lets you perform various tasks even with 5% battery life.
product_description.16.5 cm (6.5) Display: The 88.7% screen-to-body ratio and the 16.5 cm (6.5) Display lets you enjoy games, videos, and more without distractions.
product_description.Diagonal Stripe Design: The Diagonal Stripe Design offers style and personality to this smartphone. Also, the slim 8.9 mm body makes it convenient to hold and use.
product_description.Powerful Octa-core Processor: The octa-core processor ensures smooth multitasking, gaming, and watching videos.
product_description.3-card Slots: This smartphone has Dual SIM slots to let you use two numbers. Also, it has a MicroSD card slot to expand the memory capacity.
product_description.8 MP AI Camera: The 8 MP AI camera with an f/2.0 aperture captures high-quality photos with improved light. Thus, even the zoomed-in photos are crystal-clear and impressive.
product_description.AI Selfie Camera: The AI Selfie camera has AI Beauty and Portrait Modes to help you capture beautiful selfies.

pros.Price: Good product in a decent price.
pros.5000 mAh Battery: The 5000 mAh battery offers a long standby time and an awesome backup.

cons.Camera: The 8MP rear camera and 5MP front camera combination is very poor and not upto the mark.
cons.Octa-core Processor: The octa core processor is slow and the performance is bad. The phone suffers from lagging issues.

summary.verdict: The realme Narzo 50i is a good phone for normal usage in this price segment.
summary.Additional Information: Bad camera quality, Supports face lock and app lock, Heating issues.
